Coming this Fall! A new jet age travel experience!
Electra/Flight
The New Lockheed Electra
will bring you a totally differ-
ent air travel experience - you'll
fly faster than ever before…yet
in vibration-free, relaxing quiet!
Save 25% in time over today's
inter-city schedules.
You choose from more frequent
Electra/ Flights... leaving from
today's close-in airports...taking
jet age air travel even to smaller
communities. (The Electra can
serve over 300 existing commer-
cial airports in the U.S. alone.)
On board, you feel at home imme-
diately in "living room" comfort.
Electra cabins are wider, more spa-
cious. Your seat is roomier, more
relaxing-you look through a big
"picture window," or stroll a broad
aisle to enjoy a friendly lounge.
Look for the jet with props
The big General Motors Allison
Prop-jet Engines are turning over.
(Note there's no quiver-no
shake!) These 4 giants are jet
turbine engines (for power and
speed) combined with 4-bladed
props (for more dependable
short-flight performance).
In the air you speed along in
serene smoothness. If "weather"
is sighted or radar-sensed ahead,
your pilot can choose the best alti-
tude or course for your comfort...
above or below storms or winds.
You can depend on scheduled
arrival and departure times.
When Electra descends for landing -
relax. The big props actually act like
"brakes"
against the air for short,
safe landings even on slick runways.
You disembark near terminals and
can carry your luggage for quicker
getaway.
You will enjoy Electra/ Flight on these leading airlines:
ANSETTANA
WROTERN
